Buddha to stop the strange events.

172
00:12:33,372 --> 00:12:36,002
Then what is the problem?

173
00:12:36,171 --> 00:12:37,711
In short,

174
00:12:39,132 --> 00:12:41,091
there is an initial
haunted Buddha statue,

175
00:12:41,591 --> 00:12:46,431
