the one in your magazine.

176
00:12:47,012 --> 00:12:49,578
When we heard the initial
haunted Buddha statue

177
00:12:49,602 --> 00:12:51,352
was excavated in Mount Cheonbo,

178
00:12:51,681 --> 00:12:54,311
